channel.title: My music (again, added a new song)
channel.description:
Hey guys! I am a singer/songwriter and had a previous topic before about my songs, but I just finished a new song entitled "Still Mine" check it out, and my other songs, Remember my Name was the previous favorite of most people. I think "Still Mine" is pretty good, the guitar portion is pretty pathetic due to me just picking it up today.
www.myspace.com/zidell
Comments and suggestions please!
~Jewsus~
